h offers practical advantage: non-invasive at-home collection accessible to severely ill patients. _Motivated by:_ @Scholz2026SleepMetabolome — first direct biochemical measurement of sleep deprivation in oral fluid, filling the long-standing gap of no objective test for sleep loss, with chronic-vs-acute dissociation as primary constraint informing ME/CFS unrefreshing sleep biomarker strategy. Post-integration adversarial review identified certainty inflation (0.35→0.20), unfalsifiable CNS fallback framing (removed), overcomplex SRI speculation (deleted), and phase-locking speculation (deleted due to logistical impossibility for severe ME/CFS patients).

